('Finance-Spain.com', 'Financial Services', 'Independent financial advisers in Spain specialising in regulated cross-border planning for expatriates. Services include international pensions (QROPS and International SIPP), Spanish-compliant investment structures, tax-efficient retirement planning, wealth management, estate and succession planning, portfolio management, and Brexit-proofing strategies. Expert advice on Spanish tax considerations including Wealth Tax and Modelo 720 declarations. Consultations delivered online nationwide via WhatsApp and video calls. Plain-English guidance on UK inheritance tax changes affecting expats, pension transfers, and tax-efficient investment solutions tailored for residents throughout mainland Spain, Balearic and Canary Islands.', 'Nationwide (Online consultations available)', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.finance-spain.com/', true, false, false, false, NOW(), NOW());
